{"tid":1553420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日散個陣我感受到勇武手足既情，多謝你地 ～～～","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:25.000Z","uid":245673,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3004e2ba5c539e93c1d45927141f797cfb3098","tid":1553420,"uid":245673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"夢境：<br />\n<br />\n大家都知啲狗係特登提早要集會收擋<br />\n特登封站，然後出動係大路9捉，9放tg<br />\n<br />\n我係沿路走（真係要跑個隻，灣仔跑到老銅sogo）個陣一路有好多手足企係啲路口位幫人撒退， 有啲就諗住整RB<br />\n<br />\n你地每一句教我地走，都係好窩心<br />\n<br />\n我真係要鄭重多謝一次勇武手足！！<br />\n全靠你地， 先令到大家見到希望<br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得今次會逼和理非行得更前， 因為有左今日經驗<br />\n<br />\n最後一句， 記住 核彈都唔撚割<br />\n或者咁講，核彈都割唔撚到呀依舖"},{"pid":"4746ad180b456b22be6db365867ddc2da41aa4ec","tid":1553420,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1085cf25cf3004184682d0b6af03c35141c56d","tid":1553420,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"今日勇武手足救番好多人<br />\n核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"2cae044fe561b98a937c368329953616a861f823","tid":1553420,"uid":245673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日勇武手足救番好多人<br />\n核彈都唔割</blockquote><br />\n絕對係， 依啲某程度真係英雄"}]}